{"tid":802174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(超雄BB)涉非禮外籍女 南亞漢再夥三同黨混戰保安","createTime":"2018-09-01T09:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T09:32:20.000Z","uid":24788,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91847ce53acefafab14d9251ac74b046e321ed41","tid":802174,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】南亞色狼非禮洋妞，夥三同黨與保安互毆五人被捕。現場為灣仔盧押道十八號地下一間酒吧外，昨日凌晨一時許，一名廿二歲外籍女子，與酒吧一名菲律賓籍男保安員閒聊，期間有四名南亞漢經過，其中一名巴籍漢疑突施「鹹豬手」偷襲外籍女，女事主不甘受辱，轉身與對方理論，保安員亦出口「幫拖」。雙方愈吵愈烈，繼而大打出手演變街頭混戰，保安員以一敵四，適時有巡警經過，見狀制止。<br />\n<br />\n拘五人 三持「行街紙」留港<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架拘捕五男，除四十歲保安員外，還有兩名巴基斯坦漢及兩名印度漢（廿四至卅七歲），四人中除一名印度漢持有香港身份證，其餘均持「行街紙」留港，而卅七歲的巴籍漢另涉嫌非禮。保安員額頭受傷，需送院治理，案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180901/00176_012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180901%2F00176_012.html&d=P3lOVsx1LOMrVFA5p5kvIwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4f51b4d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180901/00176_012.html</a>"},{"pid":"0b5f91b9bc078f32dcd8102afd40846700eb452e","tid":802174,"uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"點解要比呢啲人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46177533e29bbee5c51ec9804a0b3d9a61e98f2c","tid":802174,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:23:14.000Z","msg":"已經算好 只係非禮唔係強姦<br />\n唔知個保安事後有冇得執返劑"},{"pid":"1cef5fd2665a0526afcc7e33e96d0a5400c0e3b3","tid":802174,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46177533e29bbee5c51ec9804a0b3d9a61e98f2c","tid":802174,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:23:14.000Z","msg":"已經算好 只係非禮唔係強姦<br />\n唔知個保安事後有冇得執返劑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"鬼妹：賓狗都好過港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522346982a67f903622ff245d4d26163cbac1884","tid":802174,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46177533e29bbee5c51ec9804a0b3d9a61e98f2c","tid":802174,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:23:14.000Z","msg":"已經算好 只係非禮唔係強姦<br />\n唔知個保安事後有冇得執返劑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"梗係有啦 未打交之前都閒聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86128c85e6d07cda257ece6d40d3121b7fd9e9f9","tid":802174,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"點解賤種垃圾都拎到行街紙？"}]}